// Vitest Snapshot v1, https://vitest.dev/guide/snapshot.html

exports[`US-DELTA-003 — delta CLI parser and help > roll delta help is localized to zh when ROLL_LANG=zh 1`] = `
"用法：roll delta <prepare|validate|conclude|status|help>

  Delta Team（host-guided）= 当前宿主主会话（隐式 Supervisor）加上由宿主 native
  能力创建的 Designer/Builder/Evaluator 子会话，通过 roll delta 驱动。Full Delta
  Team = 用 Roll 通用适配器独立编排的多 agent / 多宿主拓扑。Roll 从不 spawn、
  resume 或配置任何会话（包括你自己的）。

  诚实边界（绝不夸大）：
    - 终止绑定是 Option C，仅 handoff：delta:terminal(handoff_ready) 不是 Done、
      不是 merge、不是 attest 裁定、也不是 DeliveryRecord。handoff 后由 owner 手动
      走既有的 delivery/PR/attest 流程。
    - 宿主 attestation 仅结构校验（token 非空/唯一且在 resolution/事件/manifest 间
      对应）；绝不证明会话新起或模型执行过。
    - preset 放在 ~/.roll/delta-team/presets.yaml（仅宿主本地配置）。
    - host-guided 成本渲染 ? (host_unobservable)——绝不估算或写零。
    - loop-autonomous + delta-team 阻塞 host_supervisor_required（不静默转换）；
      loop-autonomous + full-delta-team 是显式 opt-in。

  宿主导引的委派生命周期命令（仅协议层；不启任何 agent）。

  roll delta prepare <story-id> --trigger host-guided|loop-autonomous --topology solo|delta-team|full-delta-team --profile standard|verified|designed --preset <id> --resolution <path> [--json]
    原子化申领委派帧与 host-delegation 租约。

  roll delta validate --delegation <id> --stage designer|builder|evaluator|peer [--json]
    经过协议校验边界验证角色阶段提交。

  roll delta conclude --delegation <id> --delivery-disposition owner_continue|owner_hold|owner_redelegate [--json]
    记录 owner 批准的终止绑定（Option C：handoff_ready/handoff_only）。

  roll delta status [--story <id>|--delegation <id>] [--json]
    从事件真相只读投影委派状态。

  roll delta help
    打印此帮助。
"
`;

exports[`US-DELTA-003 — delta CLI parser and help > roll delta help prints EN usage with all subcommands and exits 0 1`] = `
"Usage: roll delta <prepare|validate|conclude|status|help>

  Delta Team (host-guided) = the current host main session (implicit Supervisor)
  plus host-native Designer/Builder/Evaluator sub-agent sessions, driven through
  roll delta. Full Delta Team = an independently orchestrated multi-agent/host
  topology using Roll's generic adapters. Roll never spawns, resumes, or
  configures any session, including yours.

  Boundaries (honest, never overclaimed):
    - Terminal binding is Option C, handoff-only: delta:terminal(handoff_ready) is
      NOT Done, a merge, an attest verdict, or a DeliveryRecord. After handoff the
      owner manually runs the existing delivery/PR/attest procedure.
    - Host attestation is structural validation only (non-empty/unique tokens that
      correspond across resolution/event/manifest); never proof of a fresh session
      or that a model executed.
    - Presets live in ~/.roll/delta-team/presets.yaml (host-local config only).
    - Host-guided cost renders ? (host_unobservable) — never estimated or zeroed.
    - loop-autonomous + delta-team blocks host_supervisor_required (no silent
      conversion); loop-autonomous + full-delta-team is explicit opt-in.

  Host-guided delegation lifecycle commands (protocol-only; no agent spawning).

  roll delta prepare <story-id> --trigger host-guided|loop-autonomous --topology solo|delta-team|full-delta-team --profile standard|verified|designed --preset <id> --resolution <path> [--json]
    Atomically claim a delegation frame and host-delegation lease.

  roll delta validate --delegation <id> --stage designer|builder|evaluator|peer [--json]
    Validate a role-stage submission through the protocol-validator boundary.

  roll delta conclude --delegation <id> --delivery-disposition owner_continue|owner_hold|owner_redelegate [--json]
    Record owner-approved terminal binding (Option C: handoff_ready/handoff_only).

  roll delta status [--story <id>|--delegation <id>] [--json]
    Read-only delegation status projection from event truth.

  roll delta help
    Print this help.
"
`;
